response.overview: 48 Seals entering the water.  49 "White People, etc." contains scenes of a man and woman picking flowers, a truck driving along a wooden track or road, people posing at a house and boarding a ship, men with cameras filming fur fox.  50 "Seals," and contains images of large groups of fur seals on rocks.  51 Scenes of rocky shorelines, birds including murres and puffins nesting on rocky cliffs, eggs in a basket, men in small boat.  52 "Our Friends," contains scenes of Pribilof fur seals. "Pribilof Bird Life" are scenes of puffins and auklets and people gathering eggs. "Blue Foxes," are scenes of fur foxes in summer and winter. Reindeer in winter, and in corral. Men working to row a boat away from a rocky shoreline and toward a larger vessel. "Winter - Snow and ice scenes in March.” "Native Church service” is a procession, then an unidentified church building.  "St. Paul Island sunset on Big Lake," and "A Bering Sea sunset."
response.title: McMillin Pribilof Films (48-52)
